title: The WANK Worm, Part 1
description: On October 16th, 1989, NASA's scientists went into work preparing to launch a spacecraft that very day.  But when they sat down to their computers, they were met with an unexpected greeting: “Your system has been officially WANKed. You talk of times of peace for all, and then prepare for war.”
